c: 10
v: 43
t: "wmin alkufaar man yanzur 'iilayk wa'iilaa 'adilat nbwtk alsadqt, wlknh la yubsir ma atak allah min nuwr al'iyman, 'afa'ant -ayha alrswl- tuqadar ealaa 'an takhluq llemy absarana yahtadun bha? fkdhlk la tuqadar ealaa hdaythm 'iidha kanuu faqdy albsyrt, wa'iinama dhlk klluh lilah whdh"